# Saphyr

<img width=100 src="./docs/files/logo.svg">

Fullstack and scalable python web framework based on uvloop.

__Goals__

- Strongly opinionated
- Fast prototyping
- Async IO
- First class interop with Rust

__Inspirations__

- Phoenix
- NodeJs

